 241:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****        Below the list of most used macros in I2C HAL driver.
 242:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c **** 
 243:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_ENABLE: Enable the I2C peripheral
 244:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_DISABLE: Disable the I2C peripheral
 245:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_GENERATE_NACK: Generate a Non-Acknowledge I2C peripheral in Slave mode
 246:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_GET_FLAG: Check whether the specified I2C flag is set or not
 247:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_CLEAR_FLAG: Clear the specified I2C pending flag
 248:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_ENABLE_IT: Enable the specified I2C interrupt
 249:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_DISABLE_IT: Disable the specified I2C interrupt
