1052:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****     (#) There are two modes of transfer:
1053:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****        (++) Blocking mode : The communication is performed in the polling mode.
1054:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****             The status of all data processing is returned by the same function
1055:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****             after finishing transfer.
1056:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****        (++) No-Blocking mode : The communication is performed using Interrupts
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Nathan\AppData\Local\Temp\ccDkh7Ha.s 			page 20


1057:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****             or DMA. These functions return the status of the transfer startup.
